Register as a user:
	curl -X "POST" http://localhost:3000/v1/register --data "email={email address}&password={password}"

Get the next integer in the sequence:
	curl http://localhost:3000/v1/next -H "Authorization: Bearer {API key}"

Get the current integer:
	curl http://localhost:3000/v1/current -H "Authorization: Bearer {API key}"

Reset the current integer:
	curl -X "PUT" http://localhost:3000/v1/current -H "Authorization: Bearer {API key}" --data "current={non-negative integer}"